item.title: Help me with no-ip!
item.dc:creator: @pizza_pie pizza pie
item.description:
@pizza_pie wrote:

okay, just go to no-ip.com and then register, then go to add ports or something on the left when you are logged in, make your own port, leave the bottom parts out, just the like 2 top parts, and then dl the No-IP DUC v2, turn it on, check your server ip and then turn on ur runserver.bat, if it doesnt work, i dont know wuts wrong

if you already registered and created your no-ip on the website, you just need to download the no-ip DUC and check your server ip before running your runserver.bat :), this is off the top of my head, tell me if it worked, if it doesnt post plz
